# Day 30 Init: Capstone — Multi-Species TP53 Gene Family Analysis — Real Biological Data
# Sources:
#   Protein sequences: UniProt reference proteomes, DNA-binding domain + flanking regions
#     Human P04637, Mouse P02340, Rat P10361, Dog Q29537, Chicken P10360,
#     Zebrafish P79734, Frog P07193, Fruit fly Q9VB32 (Dmp53)
#   Domain boundaries: InterPro/Pfam annotations for p53 family
#   Species divergence: TimeTree.org estimated divergence times

mkdir("data")
mkdir("data/output")

# --- Real TP53 ortholog protein sequences from UniProt ---
# Each is the actual amino acid sequence covering transactivation + DNA-binding domain
# Truncated to ~200-300 residues for practical analysis

